---
import '../../styles/global.css';
const nav=['Overview','Organisations','Projects','Agents','Automations','Connectors','API keys','MCP','Observability','Settings'];
---
<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"/><title>Platform | bapX</title><link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg"/></head><body><div class="platform-shell"><aside><a class="brand" href="https://bapx.in/">bapX</a><button class="switcher">Bapx Media Hub <span>⌄</span></button><nav>{nav.map((item,i)=><a class={i===0?'active':''} href={`#${item.toLowerCase().replaceAll(' ','-')}`}>{item}</a>)}</nav><div class="profile"><span>BM</span><div><strong id="account-name">Business owner</strong><small id="account-email">Account</small></div></div></aside><main><header><div><p class="mono-label">PLATFORM</p><h1>Business overview</h1></div><a class="bapx-pill bapx-pill-primary" href="https://bapx.in/signup/">New business</a></header><section class="metrics"><article><span>Agents created</span><strong>0</strong></article><article><span>Automations created</span><strong>0</strong></article><article><span>Connected platforms</span><strong>0</strong></article><article><span>Projects</span><strong>0</strong></article></section><section class="panel"><div class="panel-head"><div><h2>Business activity</h2><p>Agent, automation, connector and project events across the last year.</p></div><button class="bapx-pill">All projects</button></div><div class="contributions" aria-label="No recorded activity yet">{Array.from({length:182},()=> <i></i>)}</div><div class="legend"><span>Less</span><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><span>More</span></div></section><section class="lower"><article class="panel"><h2>Projects</h2><p>No projects yet. Projects created inside this business will appear here with their agent and automation status.</p><button class="bapx-pill">Create project</button></article><article class="panel"><h2>Observability</h2><p>Choose a business or subproject to inspect agent operations, workflow runs, errors and connected services.</p><button class="bapx-pill">Open observability</button></article></section></main></div><script is:inline>fetch('/api/auth/session').then(r=>r.ok?r.json():Promise.reject()).then(({account})=>{document.querySelector('#account-name').textContent=account.name;document.querySelector('#account-email').textContent=account.email;}).catch(()=>location.href='https://bapx.in/login/');</script></body></html>
<style>
body{margin:0;background:#0a0a0a;color:#fff}.platform-shell{display:grid;grid-template-columns:260px 1fr;min-height:100vh}aside{border-right:1px solid #212327;padding:24px 16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.brand{font-size:24px;margin:0 10px 28px}.switcher{background:#191919;color:#fff;border:1px solid #363a3f;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;text-align:left;display:flex;justify-content:space-between}nav{display:grid;gap:3px;margin-top:20px}nav a{padding:10px 12px;border-radius:8px;color:#dadbdf}nav a.active{background:#1a1c20;color:#fff}.profile{margin-top:auto;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;padding:12px}.profile>span{display:grid;place-items:center;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;color:#0a0a0a}.profile div{display:grid}.profile small{color:#7d8187}main{padding:44px 5vw}main>header,.panel-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}h1{font-size:48px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.04em;margin:8px 0 34px}.metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);border:1px solid #212327;border-radius:8px}.metrics article{padding:24px;border-right:1px solid #212327}.metrics article:last-child{border:0}.metrics span{color:#7d8187}.metrics strong{display:block;font-size:36px;font-weight:400;margin-top:16px}.panel{border:1px solid #212327;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;margin-top:24px;background:#111}.panel h2{font-weight:400;margin:0 0 8px}.panel p{color:#7d8187}.contributions{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(26,1fr);gap:5px;margin-top:28px}.contributions i,.legend i{aspect-ratio:1;background:#212327;border-radius:2px}.legend{display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;align-items:center;gap:5px;color:#7d8187;font-size:12px;margin-top:10px}.legend i{width:12px}.legend i:nth-of-type(2){background:#3b5d4c}.legend i:nth-of-type(3){background:#4d815f}.legend i:nth-of-type(4){background:#64a978}.lower{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px}.lower .panel{min-height:170px}@media(max-width:800px){.platform-shell{grid-template-columns:1fr}aside{display:none}main{padding:24px}.metrics{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.metrics article{border-bottom:1px solid #212327}.lower{grid-template-columns:1fr}.contributions{grid-template-columns:repeat(14,1fr)}}
.brand{display:block;width:112px;height:38px;font-size:0;background:url('/brand/bapx-logo-main.svg') center/contain no-repeat}
</style>
